Let Me Tinyurl That For You :
Version: v2

This is my first proper plugin, if you need anything added to it.. please let me know :)
 
Commands:
 /url [url] [alias] 
 
Features:
- Allows you to shorten your URL's before sending them ingame.
- Shortens URL's that are too long in chat.

Config: 
- No Config!

Download The Plugin:
http://dev.bukkit.org/server-mods/lmturltfy/files/
 
Changelog:

Version 2
- Added Listener and Cleaned up Code.
Version 0.1
- Plugin Released!

